Leeds Infirmary has suspended Dr Ferrie and the General Medical Council has withdrawn his registration, meaning he cannot practice as a doctor.

Last night Mr Ferrie’s lawyer said: ‘Dr Colin Ferrie is co-operating with the West Yorkshire Police investigation. He has no further comment to make.’

